{"tid":2273840,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"二人涉在去年富康花園「私了」懲教員 承認暴動及有意圖傷人 胡雅文押後至11月27日判刑","createTime":"2020-11-06T04:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T16:00:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea1400ddbaecf9662663faeb1da1db1a55c16af","tid":2273840,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/f60e912cdeafaf5e7fd6c2c6818951d7/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200402/_2020040216111466960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2Ff60e912cdeafaf5e7fd6c2c6818951d7%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200402%2F_2020040216111466960.jpg&h=62476011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11057&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8vaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=55b946c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11057</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第廿八庭 <br />\n#胡雅文法官 #1109將軍澳<br />\n#聆取對控罪的回答<br />\nD1:⿈(29), D2:陳(58)<br />\n🛑二人已還押近一年<br />\n<br />\n各被告共同面對兩項控罪：<br />\n(1)暴動<br />\n(2)有意圖傷人<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n(1) 於2019年11月9日，在將軍澳唐明街富康花園一座外，與其他不知名人士參與暴動<br />\n(2) 於同日同地，與其他不知名人士一同意圖使X身體受嚴重傷害，而非法及惡意傷害X（受害人受匿名令保護<br />\n<br />\n🙇&zwj;♂️兩名被告承認控罪🙇&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n📌D1 求情：<br />\n暴動罪在2019年6月前並非常見罪行，亦沒有量刑指引，邀請法庭參考2016年的旺角暴動案判刑作參考<br />\nCACC 164/2018 7年 <br />\n<br />\n被告人並非有預謀有準備參與是次暴動，純粹(participated by chance)。而且案發時間是凌晨02:00，持續時間短暫(由00:30至03:00) 當時交通、人流稀疏。對公共秩序的影響、損害、暴力程度、規模，以暴動來說不是最嚴重，較旺角案輕微。 <br />\n<br />\n被告希望法庭就暴動罪以4年半作量刑起點，有意圖而傷人則判處以不多於3年的即時監禁，兩項控罪同期執行，並給予完整的1/3刑期扣減。 <br />\n<br />\n📌D2求情<br />\n他曾經嘗試令埸面冷靜下來，但情緒受酒精及現場人士影響，一時失控犯下本案罪行&hellip;&hellip;受害人x傷勢雖然不是輕微，但懇請法庭不要以6-7年作量刑起點。在整個襲擊過程中，D2沒有使用任何武器，他的參與性遠不及現場的其他人士<br />\n<br />\n呈上6封由被告本人，家人及前僱主撰寫的求情信<br />\n<br />\n押後至 11月27日 10:00於區域法院判刑，期間會為D1索取精神科報告及背景報告<br />\n<br />\n🛑各被告繼續還押"},{"pid":"1976182c79f035ffcd5573faaa8bb2aaf4083d60","tid":2273840,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccc4f8874ca534ed682e5c00c8ab6b76550c57b","tid":2273840,"uid":113498,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"打交都係暴動 咁元朗幾個黑警宵夜打交都係暴動啦"},{"pid":"41036113c854e902bdb39d34bc321a5cdb33157a","tid":2273840,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係懲教喎⋯⋯唔係狗喎"},{"pid":"c051aa2bcd25a4caea1ad2ed920ccd9cba56cf2b","tid":2273840,"uid":252920,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"41036113c854e902bdb39d34bc321a5cdb33157a","tid":2273840,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係懲教喎⋯⋯唔係狗喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:41:38.000Z","msg":"不用分得那麼細"},{"pid":"4b3c9e3821d48f2300bac163e312d998f7b5ac57","tid":2273840,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:42:10.000Z","msg":"胡雅文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e48c13ae3bfaa99727179244af6b569784bb7f9","tid":2273840,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"41036113c854e902bdb39d34bc321a5cdb33157a","tid":2273840,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係懲教喎⋯⋯唔係狗喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:42:47.000Z","msg":"懲教係入面無分蝦手足？<br />\n<br />\nON <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafaab5824b780e105fe0e65315c234cea1ab33f","tid":2273840,"uid":353267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c051aa2bcd25a4caea1ad2ed920ccd9cba56cf2b","tid":2273840,"uid":252920,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"41036113c854e902bdb39d34bc321a5cdb33157a","tid":2273840,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係懲教喎⋯⋯唔係狗喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:41:38.000Z","msg":"不用分得那麼細"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"懲教工作 日日翻工打人 屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689df118158aa7c1c24cbb3a5c3bf4f30a7191a3","tid":2273840,"uid":36995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b3c9e3821d48f2300bac163e312d998f7b5ac57","tid":2273840,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:42:10.000Z","msg":"胡雅文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"今次死得<br />\n4年起跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7954cb9bd33dffa7c3c1d70f8d00e98dd8877c7","tid":2273840,"uid":8308,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"41036113c854e902bdb39d34bc321a5cdb33157a","tid":2273840,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係懲教喎⋯⋯唔係狗喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"佢地暴力傾向仲嚴重過狗"},{"pid":"82deb41abff755090803bc9b8276528e542c757c","tid":2273840,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政治檢控 死全家"},{"pid":"cba046ebcc8a948c315e