"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b966fd307f620eb6ed946fd73e8c157f726d166d","tid":2273840,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"代表29歲女子的大律師透露，黃乃三子之母，過往有精神病病史，被捕後發現她罹患精神分裂症，但相信其犯案並非由病症引致。馮大狀強調黃參與程度較低，遠不如2016年旺角暴動案中的梁天琦等人，她亦非有預謀行事，望法庭考慮以4年半及不多於3年作為兩罪的量刑起點。<br />\n<br />\n至於59歲的士司機，大律師表示，陳起初嘗試「降溫」，惟其後被現場氣氛及酒精影響，最終未能自制犯案。<strong><span class=\"red\">胡雅文法官聞言指，除非有醫生報告證明上述誘因，否則不會接受。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n案發於去年‪11月9日‬凌晨12時半，逾20名示威者聚集將軍澳富康花園1座外，悼念周梓樂離世，其間高喊「香港人加油」及「黑警」。約兩小時後，男街坊X被嘈醒，遂下樓投訴群眾擾人清夢，並報警處理。示威者見狀即圍住X，陳更捉住X的手，圖阻其離開，突然，X被推倒在地，隨即被10人，包括黃及陳圍毆5至10分鐘。警方其後到場驅散及拘捕兩名被告。<br />\n<br />\nX事後被送往醫院治理，他左眼眉、額頭、左膝、左手同告受傷，共縫13針；額頭、臉部、右胸部及上肢均有挫傷，留院3天後出院。據悉，X現仍會感到痛楚，不時被惡夢纏繞，可如常上班，但不得從事劇烈運動。"},{"pid":"8e118cb3847d4a9b023e8226b6dd760b15b2d35d","tid":2273840,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"認罪果D都唔駛點幫"},{"pid":"6c916b0e925e8ccaa1d9d36b56f74ec652f11869","tid":2273840,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"<em>情緒受酒精影響.....</em><br />\n<br />\n咁佢被捕當時有無得要求吹波仔???<br />\n但唔係駕車人仕, 又好似....未必有得吹.?<br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔識..."},{"pid":"e15bfe587ca841583147eb982df96dfcf837c374","tid":2273840,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:11:52.000Z","msg":"黃乃三子之母，過往有精神病病史<br />\n<br />\n搞到三個仔女無左媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12bc6ef20e44099e52ae15684673de8e55dab31","tid":2273840,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ccc4f8874ca534ed682e5c00c8ab6b76550c57b","tid":2273840,"uid":113498,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"打交都係暴動 咁元朗幾個黑警宵夜打交都係暴動啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:36:55.000Z","msg":"行出街已經係暴動"},{"pid":"7b7fbe452c5f7c7250285aaddf394082c99f9ff0","tid":2273840,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:44:16.000Z","msg":"先砌你坐一年,坐到無晒意志唔打落去,還柙個制度真係玩撚晒"},{"pid":"6708b7265f64ee85b9179581bd5d4c61a6d6c0ad","tid":2273840,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E8%AA%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E8%93%84%E6%84%8F%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E8%2593%2584%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8vaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=a3ed1c20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E8%2593%2584%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&h=3edad72e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E8%AA%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E8%93%84%E6%84%8F%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4/</a>"},{"pid":"4bd9f9c027075926fea772bea73d356ab1214c64","tid":2273840,"uid":226085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}